sub_title: Chief Digital Officer at Damen Shipyards Group
summary:
I'm an experienced executive, and knows how to transform a company. I have worked for over 20 years in various executive management positions.

After my graduation in economics I pursued a career in the ICT Consulting industry. Between 1996 and January 2013 I worked in different positions at various companies. My primary focus in these positions was business / IT transformations, consulting, commercial and operational management. In 2013, I started as CIO at Damen Shipyards Group, managing the digital transformation and supporting the company growth by structuring the global information and setting high standards on the availability, security and accessibility of Damen’s IT infrastructure.

With a strong focus, on innovation-, program-, change- and operational management I'm the driver for digital transformation and a professional provider of high-quality digital solutions and services. This results in improved productivity, better customer experience, new revenue streams and new business models. 

I have an high level of understanding of:

Strategy development
Digital transformation and change
Organisation and capabilities
Digital strategy and business alignment 
Digital and IT  governance
Project and portfolio management
Infrastructure and applications
(IT) security and risk  

Specialties: 
Chief Digital Officer (CDO), Chief Information Officer (CIO), Digital Strategy, Digital & Business Transformation, Change management (People, process, technology), Customer Experience, Business Alignment, Digital Governance, Digital Factory, Cyber Security, Big Data, IoT, Analytics, CRM, ERP, PLM, HRM, Outsourcing
